<div class="box">
  <h3>The Club Dashboard</h3>
  <p>
  The Club Dashboard will allow you to look at certain operational
  aspects of the club and perform some operations. The right side
  will allow you to navigate to each of the items below from any
  club operation.
  <h4><%= link_to "Offices", club_offices_path %></h4>
  <p>
  This section allows you to look at the offices of the
  club and see its officers. If you have administrative privileges
  you can assign current officers.
  <h4><%= link_to "Activities", club_activities_path %></h4>
  <p>
  This section allows you to look at the Official Activities of the club.
  From there, you can see the current and past chairs of the activity, and
  get to the leaderships and its that each Activity maintains.
  <h4><%= link_to "Leaderships", club_leaderships_path %></h4>
  <p>
  This section contains the Official Leaderships, of which each leadership
  belongs to a certain activity. This will allow you to see the active
  leaders in that leadership and activity.
  <h4><%= link_to "Accounts", acct_accounts_path %></h4>
  <p>
  This section contains the "Chart of Accounts", which keeps track of
  the financial aspects of the club.
